data.description: Step into a beautifully revamped log home that effortlessly marries rustic charm with modern comfort, nestled within White Oak's friendly and well-established neighborhood. Originally constructed in 1983, this residence has undergone a remarkable transformation that has brought it to the forefront of contemporary living. In 2019, a comprehensive revitalization project breathed new life into every aspect of this home. The updates were far-reaching, with a complete overhaul of the electrical wiring ensuring safety and efficiency, while modern PEX plumbing was seamlessly integrated to enhance functionality throughout the property. The installation of a new A/C unit and water heater guarantees year-round comfort. Interior enhancements were equally impressive. The kitchen received a stylish makeover, boasting new appliances that effortlessly combine form and function. Thoughtfully placed new lighting fixtures not only elevate the ambiance but also add a touch of sophistication. Bathrooms were not left behind, as new toilets, tubs, and showers showcase contemporary design and luxury. Attention to detail extends to the home's exterior, where new gutters and windows contribute both to aesthetics and structural integrity. New doors and vanities add a touch of modern elegance, harmonizing with the fresh kitchen cabinets and countertops. A fresh coat of paint, both inside and out, revitalizes the entire property. Beyond aesthetics, practical improvements were made too. A discreet French drain installation in the backyard ensures effective water management, while a new roof installed in 2021 provides added peace of mind. Set on an expansive half-acre lot within a community with a one-way entry/exit design, this White Oak gem seamlessly blends classic architecture with modern living. The master bedroom, situated on the upper floor, offers a peaceful retreat. Meanwhile, a versatile loft area with French doors leading to a charming deck enhances the home's functional space. It's a home where tradition meets innovation, offering a glimpse into the future of comfortable, stylish living within a well-loved neighborhood. Your move-in ready Roughneck residence awaits!
